{"tid":1682982,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"不如講下有咩黃店需要幫助？","createTime":"2019-10-30T11:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:34:43.000Z","uid":9394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ace389fe1aa7cc0a1fd959fbce2762df1a40daf","tid":1682982,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"見個個都去龍門加滕屋<br />\n唔係唔好 但太多人<br />\n大家不如分享下有邊啲黃店唔太掂 需要幫手 <br />\n等大家去救下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e2338751912740812aae0dc7012509409cf0dd","tid":1682982,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"WhatsGap <br />\n去啲冇名氣既"},{"pid":"38806061fac2d65a031eed8b5a031514e9a0468f","tid":1682982,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"打擊偽黃店最佳辦法－黃店確認書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1682977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1682977</a><br />\n<br />\n如搞一樣嘢叫黃店確認書，要求黃店要貼係當眼處，如果唔係唔當你係黃店<br />\n<br />\n黃店確認書：<br />\n<br />\n我的店鋪不會播放CCTVB維穩電視台<br />\n我的店鋪不會張貼親共派或建制區議會候選人的宣傳單張<br />\n我的店鋪不會歡迎黑警光顧<br />\n我的店舖不會使用支付寶，Wechat Pay，銀聯等受中共控制的付款系統<br />\n<br />\n我的店鋪會擁護民主自由人權普世價值<br />\n並認同「光復香港，時代革命」，「天滅中共，全黨死清光」<br />\n以及「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n1。 實現「真雙普選」<br />\n2。撤銷被捕示威者控罪<br />\n3。撤回示威「暴動」定性<br />\n4。成立獨立調查委員會，解散重組警隊<br />\n5。全面撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案<br />\n<br />\n我的店鋪會預留空間，及容許食客和店員張貼與運動有關文宣及海報<br />\n我的店鋪會鼓勵職員播放與反送中有關的歌曲，主持人之網絡電台，短片（如香城教育電視，大紀元新聞，蘋果日報動新聞等）<br />\n我的店鋪會願意聘用前線因參加抗爭而被政府拘捕的義士<br />\n<br />\n我的店鋪會將確認書張貼在店舖外當眼處，以示識別。<br />\n<br />\n我的店鋪承諾會提供良好服務態度，優質食品，合理價格，為香港人服務，如食品或服務質素未如理想，或違反以上承諾，食店有幾會從「米豬連」名單剔除，以確保黃色經濟圈商家質素。<br />\n<br />\n負責人簽署：<br />\n日期："},{"pid":"aa62ca168d3460f7ea411f4dd6d85b7bca29bc03","tid":1682982,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11e2338751912740812aae0dc7012509409cf0dd","tid":1682982,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"WhatsGap <br />\n去啲冇名氣既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"真係唔知邊度無名氣 同埋都幾難搵（個人認為）<br />\n大家有貨既不如建議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0647a18a34e7139973f2390a7ae36caba9c460e5","tid":1682982,"uid":54833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"all day 靚湯！ MIHk 睇，應該真係要幫！"},{"pid":"97d5bdf561268f5fbe290f2b6cc768870bd128eb","tid":1682982,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"邊區？"},{"pid":"531bd00681b3897de4e48ebc33d6903442d90448","tid":1682982,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"觀塘：  在家 <br />\n<br />\n牛角：  茶理史<br />\n<br />\n正宗黃店"},{"pid":"fae98006c0d72a8f615e92b69ae9805624f1f183","tid":1682982,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d5bdf561268f5fbe290f2b6cc768870bd128eb","tid":1682982,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"邊區？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"都可以 集思廣益"},{"pid":"3dcc0c18e9eacafdda745999fc450cddfd828043","tid":1682982,"uid":24356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"添福對面馬路仲有間混醬坊<br />\n不妨係混醬坊買啲野過去添福邊排隊邊食"},{"pid":"d94cdb4a793c8e6a2d8ac5630569e7a003fd5461","tid":1682982,"uid":275307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"一齊建立良心經濟圈！<br />\n自己香港自己救啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以follow呢個良心食評ig同埋多d投稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有黃店食評 記得要推埋比啲港豬朋友follow啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地最鐘意做foodie打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0FXvq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0FXvq4.jpg&h=dbb13c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiBxDsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiBxDsG.jpg&h=67ac383b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以上文宣均已獲原作者授權</span>"}]}